{"tid":2391460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"從今以後 32875就係手足嘅暗號","createTime":"2021-02-02T08:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T15:53:54.000Z","uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82e6967a0d2e49373da39fe3c061fe287d575a82","tid":2391460,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"經過今次戰役，「32875」對我地呢班手足黎講就成為咗推翻極權嘅終極目標。<br />\n日後喺街撞到手足，只要互相點頭，然後輕輕講一聲「32875」。大家心裡都清楚明白，呢個或者係遙不可及嘅夢想，但係起碼我地嘗試過。或者依家同其他人講出呢個目標只會惹來世人嘅嘲笑。佢地唔會明白我地一班手足喺股壇辛辛苦苦搏殺嘅事蹟係幾咁熱血。我地團結一致對抗敵人，換來係政商界聯合抵抗，用不公義嘅手法同不實嘅指控壓逼我地。不過唔緊要，我堅信只要繼續Strong hold手上嘅GME，總有一日正義會得以伸張。<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><br />\n呢一句「32875」，暗示我地仍未放棄！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7d406f7a31d627028e199d02fb6324e68ff37e02","tid":2391460,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">32857</span>"},{"pid":"2c1784d16019faf73f0cb454ab9a685c1eaf2b3d","tid":2391460,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>32857</strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"54f7c2897b6a1483f1f70961a43088a1202fa25e","tid":2391460,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"32857"},{"pid":"214e7e5046dcff6282f443367f124cce4215bf04","tid":2391460,"uid":364041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"你地慢慢sh 今晚再跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed82d1f7b978297278bf4bbac4bda5aeeb72d6c9","tid":2391460,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"32.875 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739a68f0445d864a8137b540a0494ae2f4a0ce5c","tid":2391460,"uid":218166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:54:33.000Z",